title: Print, "Design for Cartouche Evoking the Sea", 1740
inscribed: On plate, upper left: A; upper right: 9; lower left: De la Joüe in.; lower center: avec privilege du Roi; lower right: N.C. Cochin Sculp.
provenance: From the Collection of Léon Decloux (D. 134)
dimensions:
Platemark: 25.5 x 19 cm (10 1/16 x 7 1/2 in.)
